R. William Petty



Dr. R. W. Petty, MD, is Executive Chairman at Exactech, Inc.
Dr. Petty was previously employed as a Member-Orthopaedic Residency Review Committee by American Medical Association. He also served on the board at American Academy of Orthopaedic Surgeons and Shands Teaching Hospitals & Clinics, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Arkansas, a graduate degree from The University of Arkansas, and a doctorate degree from The University of Arkansas.



